description:
@emi is going to be finishing up my work on the unleash client this sprint. This card is to integrate the new feature flags system and make sure everything still works on the app.

The backend is currently the coordinator, but we should make sure that the native apps still works. The app should simply respond to boolean values from the api.

```json
{
  "features": {
    "pro": false,
    "wire-v2": true
  }
}
```
